{"name":{"entry":101,"name":"Al-Qari'ah","meaning":"The Calamity"},"verses":[{"arabic":" ٱلْقَارِعَةُ","translation":"The (Day) of Noise and Clamour:","transliteration":"AlqariAAa"},{"arabic":"مَا ٱلْقَارِعَةُ","translation":"What is the (Day) of Noise and Clamour?","transliteration":"Ma alqariAAa"},{"arabic":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلْقَارِعَةُ","translation":"And what will explain to thee what the (Day) of Noise and Clamour is?","transliteration":"Wama adraka ma alqariAAa"},{"arabic":"يَوْمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلْفَرَاشِ ٱلْمَبْثُوثِ","translation":"(It is) a Day whereon men will be like moths scattered about,","transliteration":"Yawma yakoonu annasu kalfarashialmabthooth"},{"arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلْجِبَالُ كَٱلْعِهْنِ ٱلْمَنفُوشِ","translation":"And the mountains will be like carded wool.","transliteration":"Watakoonu aljibalu kalAAihnialmanfoosh"},{"arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتْ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","translation":"Then, he whose balance (of good deeds) will be (found) heavy,","transliteration":"Faamma man thaqulat mawazeenuh"},{"arabic":"فَهُوَ فِى عِيشَةٍ رَّاضِيَةٍ","translation":"Will be in a life of good pleasure and satisfaction.","transliteration":"Fahuwa fee AAeeshatin radiya"},{"arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنْ خَفَّتْ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","translation":"But he whose balance (of good deeds) will be (found) light,-","transliteration":"Waamma man khaffat mawazeenuh"},{"arabic":"فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٌ","translation":"Will have his home in a (bottomless) Pit.","transliteration":"Faommuhu hawiya"},{"arabic":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهْ","translation":"And what will explain to thee what this is?","transliteration":"Wama adraka ma hiya"},{"arabic":"نَارٌ حَامِيَةٌۢ","translation":"(It is) a Fire Blazing fiercely!","transliteration":"Narun hamiya"}]}